com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport

Class CardProvenance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport.CardProvenance

  • public final class CardProvenance
extends Object
    The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in i2 Analyze contains.

    Provenance enables i2 Analyze to determine whether two pieces of data have the same origin, and to retrieve data from an external source some time after it was first stored on a Card.

    Since:
    4.0
